Params: {1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory93.png'}
{2: 'Evan', 3: 'Why are you all hurting Miss Rosetta?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Evan', 3: "Why... Why are you hurting someone who's trying to protect you?!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Sailor', 3: 'Quiet, you little brat!', 4: '1'}
{3: 'A sailor grabs Evan by his collar.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Sailor', 3: "You still don't get it, do you?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Sailor', 3: 'The Forest Guard were traitors to the Union.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Sailor', 3: 'They were given mechanical bodies and exceedingly long lifespans to protect our borders as atonement for their crimes!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Sailor', 3: 'But her cowardly remarks just now are just another act of treason against the ARU!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Sailor', 3: 'Are you still going to defend her?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'Enough.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'At least return to the forest first, please.', 4: '1'}
{3: "Evan frees himself from the man's grip, and lands on the ground."}
{2: 'Evan', 3: 'Everything I said was true! I saw it with my own eyes!', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Evan', 3: "But I won't leave, Miss Rosetta! I want to stay and fight with everyone else!", 4: '2'}
{2: 'α', 3: 'Can you smell the stench of the Punishing Virus in the wind? The tide of Corrupted is almost here.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'α', 3: 'These people are running out of options.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'α', 3: 'But... you still have a choice.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'α', 3: 'If the Narwhal dies alongside these humans for nothing...', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: "Commandant, Rosetta's M.I.N.D. is beginning to destabilize! Corruption level is surging!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'α', 3: "I'll cut straight to the chase.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'α', 3: 'As long as you help me eliminate the interference and tame the Narwhal, I promise that he will remain unharmed...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'α', 3: 'Then I will take him and leave this place forever.', 4: '1'}
{3: "Alpha turns and hops onto the Narwhal's back."}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: "Commandant, I... we can't let her get away!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: "Who knows when we'll see her again if we allow her to leave?", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: "Lucia, your new frame has entered the atmosphere. I've adjusted the landing coordinates within proximity of the Narwhal.", 4: '1'}
{3: 'But right as Lucia takes a step forward—'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'Stop... right there.', 4: '1'}
